(VC Track supported by Kernel & Dimensional) Tj
T*
T*
(## Problem) Tj
T*
(Robots can perceive and plan, but when ambiguity occurs humans must intervene.) Tj
T*
(Today intervention is low-bandwidth \(keyboard/dashboard\). This does not scale.) Tj
T*
T*
(ThoughtLink decodes non-invasive brain signals into discrete, high-level robot) Tj
T*
(instructions \(not joint control\), enabling fast one-to-many supervision.) Tj
T*
T*
(## Data & Command Space) Tj
T*
(Dataset: `robot_control_data/data/*.npz` \(15s chunks; cue starts at 3s\).) Tj
T*
(Signals: 6-channel EEG at 500 Hz \(time-series\).) Tj
T*
(Canonical actions: `STOP`, `LEFT`, `RIGHT`, `FORWARD`, `BACKWARD`.) Tj
T*
T*
(## Approach \(Strictly Aligned to Requirement_doc.md\)) Tj
T*
(1\) Intent decoder \(fast baseline first\)) Tj
T*
(- Windowing: 0.5s windows, 0.1s hop \(real-time compatible\).) Tj
T*
(- Features \(per channel\):) Tj
T*
(  log-variance + log bandpower \(theta 4-8, alpha 8-13, beta 13-30\) +) Tj
T*
(  relative bandpower \(4-30\). For 6 channels => 42-D features.) Tj
T*
(- Model \(hierarchical\):) Tj
T*
(  Stage1: Binary Logistic Regression \(REST vs MOVE\).) Tj
T*
(  Stage2: Softmax Regression \(LEFT/RIGHT/FORWARD/BACKWARD on MOVE windows\).) Tj
T*
(- Optional baseline correction: `pre_cue` delta features to reduce drift.) Tj
T*
T*
(2\) Temporal stability & false-trigger suppression \(core hackathon focus\)) Tj
T*
(- EWMA smoothing + hysteresis thresholds + debouncing over time.) Tj
T*
(- Parameters: `p_move_on/off`, `move_on/off_k`, `p_dir`, `dir_k`, `dir_off_k`,) Tj
T*
(  `dir_margin`, `stop_on_dir_uncertain`.) Tj
T*
(- Auto-tuning \(`examples/tune_stability.py`\) searches parameters under explicit) Tj
T*
(  constraints to avoid degenerate "all STOP" solutions.) Tj
T*
T*
(3\) Multi-subject generalization \(ELLA-style shared basis\)) Tj
T*
(- Learn a shared linear basis from non-target subjects; fit target with small) Tj
T*
(  calibration sessions to adapt quickly.) Tj
T*
(- Implemented in `examples/train_ella_intent.py` \(basis task = session/subject\).) Tj
T*
T*
(## Evaluation \(Real-Time & Closed-Loop\)) Tj
T*
(We evaluate in closed-loop replay \(50 Hz\) and in MuJoCo sim:) Tj
T*
(- `false_rate_global`: fraction of REST time where predicted action is non-STOP.) Tj
T*
(- `onset_latency`: time from cue start \(3s\) to first non-STOP during MOVE.) Tj
T*
(- `switches_per_min`: temporal stability / flicker proxy.) Tj
T*
(- `inference_ms`: per-tick inference latency \(must support real time\).) Tj
T*
T*
(Internal KPI targets \(for demo + scalability reasoning\):) Tj
T*
(- Demo pass: `false_rate_global <= 0.05`.) Tj
T*
(- 100-robot scale: `false_rate_global <= 0.01` \(otherwise errors accumulate\).) Tj
T*
T*
(## Example Result \(Illustrative\)) Tj
T*
(Subject `37dfbd76`, session `5c71e7df`, update_hz=50 \(ELLA + stabilizer\):) Tj
T*
(- `false_rate_global=0.043` \(meets demo pass\), `onset_latency_mean=2.50s`,) Tj
T*
(  `inference_ms_mean~0.37ms` \(CPU, numpy\).) Tj
T*
(Tradeoff observed: stricter false-trigger settings reduce `move_coverage`.) Tj
T*
T*
(## Demo Commands \(3-5 minutes\)) Tj
T*
(1\) Oracle control \(proves sim pipeline\): `examples/intent_policy.py --mode oracle`) Tj
T*
(2\) Model control \(decoder + stabilizer\): `examples/intent_policy.py --mode model`) Tj
T*
(3\) Batch report \(not cherry-picking\): `examples/eval_closed_loop.py --top-k 5`) Tj
T*
T*
